original:
<color_red>Brings your Cataclysm experience into a hellish nightmare…</color>
<color_dark_gray>◆ Not recommended for newbs ◆</color>

<color_light_cyan>Note that this mod is currently in <color_light_green>stable</color> state. Bugs rarely appears, but if you encounter one or a recent CDDA update has caused an error, feel free to notify the maintainer by creating an issue on its GitHub repository or by sending a DM on Discord.</color>
translation:
<color_red>将你的大灾变经历带入地狱般的噩梦… </color>
<color_dark_gray> ◆不推荐新手使用◆</color>

 <color_light_cyan>注意，这个mod目前处于<color_light_green>稳定</color>状态。bug很少出现，但是如果您遇到一个bug或者最近的CDDA更新导致了一个bug，请随时通过在其GitHub存储库中创建一个问题或者通过发送一个关于报错的DM来通知维护者。</color>

original:
"Feed" the bio-organic exoskeleton by activating <color_light_blue>Feed</color> command under the spellcasting tab (undefined by default). Alternatively, you can activate the <color_yellow>Metabolic Distribution</color> bionic, but it is advisable to use it only if you ran out of flesh.

To complete this mission, obtain a <color_light_green>blob glob</color>. It's the main ingredient in creating food for your suit.
translation:
通过激活“施法”选项卡下的<color_light_blue>喂养</color>命令（默认情况下未设定）来“喂养”生物有机外骨骼。或者，你可以激活<color_yellow>代谢供能</color>CBM，但只有当你的肉类用完了才建议使用它。

想要完成喂食，需要<color_light_green>变形怪糊</color>。它是为你的生物有机外骨骼制作食物的主要成分。

Activate to perform:
<color_cyan><color_pink>[FORM]</color> Replenish</color> - <color_yellow>800 moves</color>/<color_light_red>5 hp (random)</color>
<color_white>* Your bone rifle creation commands the vessel to form a stack of bone needles by processing the user's flesh.</color>

利用肉体的多功能细胞重建而成。这种生物有机步枪向目标发射针状骨弹。它没有触发机制，步枪只响应用户的命令。一旦它接收到输入，它就会在弹膛中产生肌腱冲击，以高速将子弹穿过它的长筒。

激活执行:
 <color_cyan> <color_pink>[表单] </color>补充- <color_yellow> 800移动/ <color_light_red> 5 hp(随机)

original:
It is currently not merged with anything. Activate to permanently merge with it.

A complex battle suit brought to existence using the latest technological advancements. Secronom exoskeleton type "Vessel" takes advantage of the flesh's adaptive cell structure and its capability to respond from one's mind. Limited in interface features, it excels on dealing any situation thanks to its morphing and forming capability.

Merging with the secronom exoskeleton type "Vessel" provides:
<color_white>Stamina regeneration: <color_light_green>+25%</color>
Maximum health: <color_light_green>+5%</color>
Metabolism: <color_light_green>-5%</color></color>
translation:
它目前没有与任何内容合并。激活以永久与其合并。

采用最新技术进步制成的复杂战斗服。Secronom外骨骼类型的“血管”利用了肉体的适应性细胞结构及其从头脑中做出反应的能力。受限于界面特性，由于其变形和成型能力，它擅长处理任何情况。

与secronom外骨骼类型“船只”相结合，可提供:
